<subSubSection lastPageId="3" lastPageNumber="56" pageId="2" pageNumber="55" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="2.[264,1323,1825,1891]" box="[264,366,1825,1850]" pageId="2" pageNumber="55">
<emphasis box="[264,366,1825,1850]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="55">Remarks</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[264,1323,1825,1891]" lastBlockId="3.[264,1323,284,390]" lastPageId="3" lastPageNumber="56" pageId="2" pageNumber="55">
This species has a Palaearctic distribution (
<bibRefCitation author="Balachowsky" box="[828,1058,1865,1891]" pageId="2" pageNumber="58" refString="Balachowsky, A. S. (1966) Entomologie Appliquee a l'agriculture, Tome II Lepidopteres, 1057 pp." type="book" year="1966">
Balachowsky 
<number box="[998,1058,1865,1891]" pageId="2" pageNumber="55" value="1966.0">1966</number>
</bibRefCitation>
) and was listed in the “ 
<taxonomicName box="[274,419,284,310]" class="Insecta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="56" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="order">Lepidoptera</taxonomicName>
of 
<collectingCountry box="[460,547,284,310]" name="Turkey" pageId="3" pageNumber="56">Turkey</collectingCountry>
” by 
<bibRefCitation author="Kocak" box="[602,769,284,310]" pageId="3" pageNumber="58" refString="Kocak, A. O. (2001) Tentative Checklist of the Turkish Lepidoptera Pt. 3 (Available from: http: // www. members. tripod. com / entlep / Checklist 3. htm." type="book chapter" year="2001">
Koçak (
<number box="[696,760,284,310]" pageId="3" pageNumber="56" value="2001.0">2001</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
. However, we found no records of this species in 
<collectingCountry box="[298,384,324,350]" name="Turkey" pageId="3" pageNumber="56">Turkey</collectingCountry>
. The host plants reported in the literature, e.g., 
<emphasis box="[971,1261,324,349]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="56">
<taxonomicName box="[971,1121,324,349]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Convolvulus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="3" pageNumber="56" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Convolvulus</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[1136,1261,324,349]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Calystegia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="3" pageNumber="56" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Calystegia</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
, and 
<emphasis box="[264,359,364,389]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="56">
<taxonomicName box="[264,355,364,389]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Ipomea" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="3" pageNumber="56" phylum="Magnoliophyta" rank="genus">Ipomea</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
all occur in 
<collectingCountry box="[506,593,364,390]" name="Turkey" pageId="3" pageNumber="56">Turkey</collectingCountry>
; therefore this species may be present.
</paragraph>
